The '''Calamari Sea''', also known as the '''Mon Calamari Sea''', was the [[Planet/Legends|planet]]-spanning [[Ocean/Legends|ocean]] located on [[Dac/Legends|Mon Calamari]]. During the [[Battle of Calamari]], [[World Devastator]]s dropped into this sea.

